{"tid":311142,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣佈嗲哋仍然心繫車仔!!","createTime":"2017-07-06T11:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T11:41:49.000Z","uid":44445,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f512d516594167a9611a82605db532709e1fad31","tid":311142,"uid":44445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T11:14:53.000Z","msg":"去到曼聯就已經即刻開始幫車仔削弱曼既力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先係以1億簽個普巴敗左曼既身家先<br />\n你估佢真係唔知普巴唔值1億咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢就係知先買, 唔係阿巴可能已經射左錢落海<br />\n<br />\n之後其實嗲哋真係做得出面左少少<br />\n佢知車仔輸完俾阿仙奴之後失哂信心<br />\n所以就專登送4粒蛋俾車仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢知自己個次做得太出面 所以之後其實都收歛左<br />\n足總盃就叫人踢鳩世三 等曼聯可以打少個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n令車仔可以晉級下一圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁做真係太高明 又唔使引人懷疑 又可以表達到自己對車仔既愛<br />\n返到去英超, 佢明知車都贏硬英超<br />\n咁為左唔好再俾人懷疑 咪直接2-0贏車仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁做佢咪可以繼續留係曼聯<br />\n為佢下一步路開路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但呢步路我都估佢唔到<br />\n就係用75m簽個盧卡古返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想當年佢用28m賣佢走 就係知盧卡古根本唔岩車仔<br />\n佢睇到新聞知道車仔班高層已經痴q左線<br />\n竟然想用1億買個唔岩車仔既人返佢心愛既車仔<br />\n佢就知道自己唔可以再忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢唔想佢心愛既車仔射錢落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就用75m幫曼聯買左個盧卡古返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嗲哋 我知好多車迷都已經唔鍾意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我今日完全明白你係幾咁愛車仔喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放心啦, 你永遠係我既special one<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望咁多位車迷都會明白 佢做咁多野都係有佢既原因架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dabdc66587242244ff2936bb29b5a7822ec67bb","tid":311142,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T11:15:40.000Z","msg":"其實睇返我覺得普巴值1億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9afc7a03588f3236c7e9870f54dacaedb4f898f1","tid":311142,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T11:16:40.000Z","msg":"嘩屌你咁都兜到"},{"pid":"a268b4f62b630c5fa3b891ca9f20c150aab298ee","tid":311142,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T11:16:59.000Z","msg":"daddy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b703764f2bd53796d6bededd866ebec6716008","tid":311142,"uid":44445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T11:18:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實睇返我覺得普巴值1億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你真心咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算佢踢得返係祖記個時咁都唔值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能係通貨膨脹, 我覺得呀朗美欺先值呢個價"},{"pid":"0955658fb8e6bb29921748b9a39c48030b5177ed","tid":311142,"uid":44445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T11:18:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>daddy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c68ff360c8aafc3d70f7d3b11db356a2dea376","tid":311142,"uid":48162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T11:29:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實睇返我覺得普巴值1億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你真心咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算佢踢得返係祖記個時咁都唔值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能係通貨膨脹, 我覺得呀朗美欺先值呢個價</blockq