es/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n迪迪尼個時係隊入邊都冇絕對正選<br />\n但迪迪尼想走, daddy知道佢將來係有料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以咪放佢去遠啲既德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知個迪迪尼又會咁想返英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n迪迪尼單野係daddy計漏左一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}